                "imageUrl": "//pic.allhistory.com/T1hFKvBXWT1RCvBVdK.jpeg?ch=178&cw=283&cx=0&cy=0",
                "summary": "<p><b>附宝</b>是<a data-id=\"591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" target=\"_blank\">黄帝</a>的母亲。</p>\n\n<p>附宝是<a data-id=\"5924a50c55b54278ac05d89f\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924a50c55b54278ac05d89f\" target=\"_blank\">有蟜氏</a>之女，后来嫁给有熊国国君<a data-id=\"592422fe55b54278ac00cd99\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/592422fe55b54278ac00cd99\" target=\"_blank\">少典</a>。附宝在<a data-id=\"591059c655b542257a025115\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/591059c655b542257a025115\" target=\"_blank\">天水</a>生下<a data-id=\"591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" target=\"_blank\">黄帝</a>，又据《<a data-id=\"59192e2f55b5421554000253\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59192e2f55b5421554000253\" target=\"_blank\">竹书纪年</a>》记载附宝郊外田间散步，见万丈光芒，&ldquo;大电绕北斗枢星，光照郊野&rdquo;，便怀孕了，二十五个月后生下黄帝。</p>\n",
