                "imageUrl": "//img.allhistory.com/5f8f00d58513910001e3989a.png",
                "summary": "<p><b>少典</b>，华夏族，汉族先祖之一，也称<strong>有熊氏</strong>，上古有熊部落的首领，《<a data-id=\"5acb4176c3666e3b9a0a4696\" href=\"/detail/5acb4176c3666e3b9a0a4696\" target=\"_blank\">国语</a>》记载其嫡子为<a data-id=\"592412a555b54278ac000238\" href=\"/detail/592412a555b54278ac000238\" target=\"_blank\">炎帝</a>神农氏和<a data-id=\"591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" href=\"/detail/591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" target=\"_blank\">黄帝</a>轩辕氏。</p>\n\n<p>《<a data-id=\"57eccf1a0bd1be0e7a8b4567\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/57eccf1a0bd1be0e7a8b4567\" target=\"_blank\">史记</a>&middot;五帝本纪》：&ldquo;黄帝者，少典之子&rdquo;。《<a data-id=\"59244cf955b54278ac02a13c\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59244cf955b54278ac02a13c\" target=\"_blank\">史记集解</a>》<a data-id=\"590fd1fe977fd51d4baf081f\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/590fd1fe977fd51d4baf081f\" target=\"_blank\">谯周</a>：&ldquo;有熊国君，少典之子也。&rdquo;《国语&middot;晋语四》：&ldquo;昔少典娶于<a data-id=\"5924a50c55b54278ac05d89f\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924a50c55b54278ac05d89f\" target=\"_blank\">有蟜氏</a>，生黄帝、炎帝&rdquo;。</p>\n",
