                "imageUrl": "//pic.allhistory.com/T1Q1DvBXhv1RCvBVdK.jpeg?ch=160&cw=160&cx=0&cy=0",
                "summary": "<p><b>嫘祖</b> （<span style=\"font-size:;\">&ldquo;嫘&rdquo;，<a data-id=\"592412be55b54278ac000328\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/592412be55b54278ac000328\" target=\"_blank\">拼音</a>：<span>l&eacute;i</span>，<a data-id=\"59105dd155b542257a02b098\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59105dd155b542257a02b098\" target=\"_blank\">注音</a>：<span>ㄌㄟˊ</span>，<a data-id=\"57c3a2c00bd1bead78a0bda4\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/57c3a2c00bd1bead78a0bda4\" target=\"_blank\">中古拟音</a>：<span class=\"IPA\" style=\"font-family: 'Charis SIL', 'Doulos SIL', 'Linux Libertine', 'Segoe UI', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Code2000', 'Gentium', 'Gentium Alternative', 'TITUS Cyberbit Basic', 'Arial Unicode MS', 'IPAPANNEW', 'Chrysanthi Unicode', 'GentiumAlt', 'Bitstream Vera', 'Bitstream Cyberbit', 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic Pro', 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; text-decoration:none!important\">lyi</span></span>）是中国上古人物，是黄帝的正妻。 《<a data-id=\"57eccf1a0bd1be0e7a8b4567\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/57eccf1a0bd1be0e7a8b4567\" target=\"_blank\">史记</a>》提到<a data-id=\"591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" target=\"_blank\">黄帝</a>娶西陵氏之女嫘祖为妻，她发明养<a data-id=\"591ab0c255b5427dfa005fcb\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/591ab0c255b5427dfa005fcb\" target=\"_blank\">蚕</a>，为&ldquo;嫘祖始蚕&rdquo;，由此开启了中国数千年养蚕和制造丝绸的历史。嫘祖是传说中的北方部落首领黄帝轩辕氏的元妃，她生了<a data-id=\"58f883bb55b54258e70003e8\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/58f883bb55b54258e70003e8\" target=\"_blank\">玄嚣</a>（少昊）、<a data-id=\"59241fee55b54278ac00a4d6\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59241fee55b54278ac00a4d6\" target=\"_blank\">昌意</a>二子。昌意娶蜀山氏女为妻<sup class=\"sup-reference\" ref-id=\"ref-1\">[1]</sup>，生高阳继承天下，这就是五帝中的&ldquo;<a data-id=\"58f883bb55b54258e70003e7\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/58f883bb55b54258e70003e7\" target=\"_blank\">颛顼</a>帝&rdquo;，后来玄嚣的孙子继承颛顼帝为<a data-id=\"5910547555b542257a01d0d2\" href=\"/detail/5910547555b542257a01d0d2\" target=\"_blank\">帝喾</a>。</p>\n\n<p>据《<a data-id=\"5924175a55b54278ac003aef\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924175a55b54278ac003aef\" target=\"_blank\">隋书</a>&middot;礼仪志》记载，北周尊嫘祖为&ldquo;先蚕&rdquo;（即始蚕之神），此后王朝立<a data-id=\"5924178255b54278ac003cb2\" href=\"/detail/5924178255b54278ac003cb2\" target=\"_blank\">先蚕坛</a>祭祀。《<a data-id=\"5924274355b54278ac0103ac\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924274355b54278ac0103ac\" target=\"_blank\">通鉴外纪</a>》记载：&ldquo;西陵氏之女嫘祖为帝之妃，始教民育蚕，治丝萝以供衣服。&rdquo;</p>\n",
