                "imageUrl": "//pic.allhistory.com/T1cVDvByKT1RCvBVdK.jpeg?ch=288&cw=268&cx=0&cy=0",
                "summary": "<p><b>女节</b>，是轩辕<a data-id=\"591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" target=\"_blank\">黄帝</a>的次妃，出自<a data-id=\"592497de55b54278ac05357e\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/592497de55b54278ac05357e\" target=\"_blank\">方雷氏</a>，相传为梳子的发明者。</p>\n\n<p><a data-id=\"592417e355b54278ac004116\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/592417e355b54278ac004116\" target=\"_blank\">皇甫谧</a>说黄帝元妃西陵氏女就是<a data-id=\"5924142255b54278ac001675\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924142255b54278ac001675\" target=\"_blank\">嫘祖</a>，生<a data-id=\"59241fee55b54278ac00a4d6\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59241fee55b54278ac00a4d6\" target=\"_blank\">昌意</a>；次妃方雷氏女就是女节，生<a data-id=\"5924174155b54278ac0039e0\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924174155b54278ac0039e0\" target=\"_blank\">青阳</a>；次妃<a data-id=\"591abdb655b5427dfa016227\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/591abdb655b5427dfa016227\" target=\"_blank\">彤鱼氏</a>女，生夷鼓，一名苍林；次妃<a data-id=\"59242bae55b54278ac01394e\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59242bae55b54278ac01394e\" target=\"_blank\">嫫母</a>。《国语》夷鼓、苍林是二人。《<a data-id=\"57c3c62b0bd1be3f7ca0bda3\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/57c3c62b0bd1be3f7ca0bda3\" target=\"_blank\">汉书</a>》古今人表<a data-id=\"591abdb655b5427dfa016227\" href=\"/detail/591abdb655b5427dfa016227\" target=\"_blank\">彤鱼氏</a>生夷鼓，<a data-id=\"57ecbaee0bd1bec6708b4567\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/57ecbaee0bd1bec6708b4567\" target=\"_blank\">司马迁</a>据《<a data-id=\"59241a0955b54278ac005a9e\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59241a0955b54278ac005a9e\" target=\"_blank\">大戴礼记</a>》，说嫘祖生昌意及玄嚣，玄嚣即青阳。皇甫谧以青阳为<a data-id=\"58f883bb55b54258e70003e8\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/58f883bb55b54258e70003e8\" target=\"_blank\">少昊</a>，乃女节所生。</p>\n\n<p>《春秋纬元命苞》说黄帝之时，女节在梦中幻觉如虹下落华渚（今<a data-id=\"5910579855b542257a021c40\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5910579855b542257a021c40\" target=\"_blank\">河北</a>盐山）巨大的<a data-id=\"5924145c55b54278ac001940\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924145c55b54278ac001940\" target=\"_blank\">流星</a>落在身上，意感而生白帝朱宣。<a data-id=\"5b36f79a303a6540ba6db6e5\" href=\"/detail/5b36f79a303a6540ba6db6e5\" target=\"_blank\">宋均</a>注称朱宣就是少昊帝。</p>\n",
