                "imageUrl": "//pic.allhistory.com/T1srWvBsE_1RCvBVdK.jpeg?ch=355&cw=268&cx=0&cy=0",
                "summary": "<p><b>昌意</b>，是<a data-id=\"591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/591e65ad977fd52c045b359e\" target=\"_blank\">黄帝</a>的一个儿子。</p>\n\n<p>黄帝有二十五个儿子，其中有二子为<a data-id=\"5924142255b54278ac001675\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924142255b54278ac001675\" target=\"_blank\">嫘祖</a>所生，长子为<a data-id=\"58f883bb55b54258e70003e8\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/58f883bb55b54258e70003e8\" target=\"_blank\">玄嚣</a>，次子昌意。据载黄帝二十九年，嫘祖于若水（雅砻江）生昌意。黄帝七十七年令昌意降居于四川若水。其后昌意娶蜀山氏女昌仆为妻，生子高阳，即帝<a data-id=\"58f883bb55b54258e70003e7\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/58f883bb55b54258e70003e7\" target=\"_blank\">颛顼</a>。后来昌意北迁至中原，建昌意城（今河南乐西北），颛顼后于黄帝崩后继位为部落首领。<sup class=\"sup-reference\" ref-id=\"ref-1\">[1]</sup></p>\n\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.98.8C.E6.84.8F.E7.9A.84.E5.90.8E.E4.BB.A3\">昌意的后代</span></h3>\n\n<p>二世：昌意，黄帝次子。三世：<a data-id=\"58f883bb55b54258e70003e7\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/58f883bb55b54258e70003e7\" target=\"_blank\">颛顼</a>，昌意之子。四世：<a data-id=\"592441ff55b54278ac02143e\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/592441ff55b54278ac02143e\" target=\"_blank\">穷蝉</a>，颛顼之子 。五世：<a data-id=\"59244aa755b54278ac028503\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59244aa755b54278ac028503\" target=\"_blank\">敬康</a>，穷蝉之子。六世：<a data-id=\"59244aa755b54278ac028504\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59244aa755b54278ac028504\" target=\"_blank\">句望</a>，敬康之子。七世：<a data-id=\"59244aa755b54278ac028505\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59244aa755b54278ac028505\" target=\"_blank\">桥牛</a>，句望之子。八世：<a data-id=\"5924424155b54278ac02178f\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924424155b54278ac02178f\" target=\"_blank\">瞽叟</a>，桥牛之子。九世：重华，瞽叟之子，即帝<a data-id=\"58f883bb55b54258e70003e2\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/58f883bb55b54258e70003e2\" target=\"_blank\">舜</a>有虞。</p>\n\n<p>另外，夏<a data-id=\"5910547355b542257a01d0b6\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5910547355b542257a01d0b6\" target=\"_blank\">禹</a>（夏朝祖先）之父<a data-id=\"58f883f555b54258e70009e9\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/58f883f555b54258e70009e9\" target=\"_blank\">鲧</a>，其父为颛顼，也是昌意的后代。<sup class=\"sup-reference\" ref-id=\"ref-2\">[2]</sup>而根据<a data-id=\"57eccf1a0bd1be0e7a8b4567\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/57eccf1a0bd1be0e7a8b4567\" target=\"_blank\">史记</a>记载匈奴与夏人同族，也可能为昌意这一系的后代。《<a data-id=\"5924131d55b54278ac00073d\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924131d55b54278ac00073d\" target=\"_blank\">山海经</a>&middot;大荒北经》也称:<a data-id=\"59242b0155b54278ac01321f\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59242b0155b54278ac01321f\" target=\"_blank\">犬戎</a>与夏人同祖,皆出于黄帝。</p>\n\n<p>根据史记记载，<a data-id=\"59094c69977fd58437202f57\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/59094c69977fd58437202f57\" target=\"_blank\">战国</a>时<a data-id=\"5910586e55b542257a022f73\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5910586e55b542257a022f73\" target=\"_blank\">秦</a>和<a data-id=\"57eb78790bd1be03248b4567\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/57eb78790bd1be03248b4567\" target=\"_blank\">赵</a>都是黄帝孙<a data-id=\"58f883bb55b54258e70003e7\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/58f883bb55b54258e70003e7\" target=\"_blank\">颛顼</a>曾孙女<a data-id=\"5924466055b54278ac024ef7\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924466055b54278ac024ef7\" target=\"_blank\">女修</a>后代<a data-id=\"5924311f55b54278ac0178f8\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924311f55b54278ac0178f8\" target=\"_blank\">大业</a>（即<a data-id=\"592426b155b54278ac00fca3\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/592426b155b54278ac00fca3\" target=\"_blank\">皋陶</a>）的后人。</p>\n\n<p>《山海经》记载：&ldquo;有北狄之国。黄帝之孙曰始均，始均生<a data-id=\"5924232a55b54278ac00cfba\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924232a55b54278ac00cfba\" target=\"_blank\">北狄</a>。&rdquo;这一说法后来被《<a data-id=\"5924130a55b54278ac000668\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924130a55b54278ac000668\" target=\"_blank\">晋书</a>》及《<a data-id=\"5924175a55b54278ac003af2\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924175a55b54278ac003af2\" target=\"_blank\">北史</a>》沿用，二书都认为鲜卑始祖也为黄帝：&ldquo;始均为<a data-id=\"5924174b55b54278ac003a61\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924174b55b54278ac003a61\" target=\"_blank\">鲜卑族</a>始祖。&rdquo;《晋书》称<a data-id=\"5910547f55b542257a01d1b4\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5910547f55b542257a01d1b4\" target=\"_blank\">慕容廆</a>，&ldquo;昌黎棘城鲜卑人也。其先有熊氏之苗裔，世居北夷，号曰<a data-id=\"5924147755b54278ac001a7f\" data-type=\"entry\" href=\"/detail/5924147755b54278ac001a7f\" target=\"_blank\">东胡</a>。&rdquo;</p>\n",
